HEADWORD: Thea
<hw>The"a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Tea</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of plants found in
China and Japan; the tea plant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ It is now commonly referred to the genus
<gen>Camellia</gen>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

